headline: Intel (NasdaqGS:INTC) Executive Shakeup: Chief Commercial Officer Resigns To Lead Kuka
summary: Intel (NasdaqGS:INTC) recently announced the resignation of its Chief Commercial Officer, Christoph Schell, and the elevation of Jason Grebe to the executive team, as the company continues to reshape its leadership. During the last quarter, Intel's stock rose 3.5%, aligning with the broader market's upward trend. headline: US weighs easing Nvidia chip curbs on UAE as Trump plans visit
summary: (Bloomberg) -- The US is weighing a potential easing of restrictions on Nvidia Corp. sales to the United Arab Emirates, according to people familiar with the matter, who said President Donald Trump could announce the start of work on a bilateral chip deal during his upcoming trip to the Gulf.
